# Devvit / TypeScript runtime

Use existing npm scripts:

```powershell
npm run build
npm run type-check
npm run dev
npm run upload
```

`npm run upload` is an intentional Devvit automation when the task is to publish or refresh the app.
Before changing upload behavior, confirm `devvit.json`, app identity, and target environment.

For Devvit API changes, use current docs and check existing compliance docs before editing.
